{"h2519a74fg603fg4c2bg883dg4372a489e41f": ["Sounds like Astarion's here to stay - and we're fine with that?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "3f4a3c47-5a66-47f2-8874-02697a4df1bc"], "h4382fef1g0525g4abdg9caagd5dc02c2e88d": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "3f4a3c47-5a66-47f2-8874-02697a4df1bc"], "h7ef2ef93gcd57g4c7egb4c1g30f22ead3f67": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "3f4a3c47-5a66-47f2-8874-02697a4df1bc"], "h647a23e8g35b8g45c9g9f08g5d3f86257921": ["I'm grateful you didn't hand me over to the hunter. Although I'm not sure the rest of the party agrees.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "3f4a3c47-5a66-47f2-8874-02697a4df1bc"], "hc260318cgc736g4f2aga04dge8116566114e": ["Seems like we're casting our lot with Astarion then. No doubts?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "3f4a3c47-5a66-47f2-8874-02697a4df1bc"], "hfa0ca2f5g1f9cg46a6g928dg562f7e79b5db": ["Astarion remains, and the hunter leaves without his quarry.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "3f4a3c47-5a66-47f2-8874-02697a4df1bc"], "h682357f4g964dg4dbcgae90g29e1e08962b4": ["  | We protected Astarion from Gur Hunter. How do we feel about it?(Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "3f4a3c47-5a66-47f2-8874-02697a4df1bc"], "h9304356ag3c3bg4712g815eg093cf7aaee8a": ["That hunter's out of the way. Astarion shouldn't have to look over his shoulder anymore.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "3f4a3c47-5a66-47f2-8874-02697a4df1bc"], "h55afca22gf179g43ccgba75g86b825bd3820": ["A vampire among us? It doesn't sit right.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "7a6571d8-5c90-4e8c-9887-d280361957e8"], "h2465eccagf05eg4f1dgbc14g49d930a421d8": ["Astarion is an unstable element. So long as he stays, we are in peril.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "7a6571d8-5c90-4e8c-9887-d280361957e8"], "haf5366d6g2410g497bgb520g5354ed6d90be": ["| I want option A (Asterion Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "7a6571d8-5c90-4e8c-9887-d280361957e8"], "h4a19fffeg7369g421dgb1eag95ecb997b6f5": ["That was a perfect opportunity to rid ourselves of a dangerous liability, and we botched it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "7a6571d8-5c90-4e8c-9887-d280361957e8"], "h418a9615g0659g4914g82b3ge263e6746295": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "7a6571d8-5c90-4e8c-9887-d280361957e8"], "had59936agfd24g495agbbcfg2fbd501bc9ea": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "7a6571d8-5c90-4e8c-9887-d280361957e8"], "h86dc2018g6c54g471cg8d89ga6c432dc72e0": ["| I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "7a6571d8-5c90-4e8c-9887-d280361957e8"], "hfdb23a7eg5af9g44eegbebfg6014db970f50": ["| 