7-4aae-aeb8-6b036f8b937f"], "hb3106726g5fe8g46a0ga4bdg9f2d635de9d6": ["Well, let's not dwell on it. We have other things to attend to.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "97379a69-0187-4aae-aeb8-6b036f8b937f"], "h012683cbg4159g4e18g938agd8ad49f63378": ["Seems things aren't so cut and dry then. But nothing more to be said for now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "97379a69-0187-4aae-aeb8-6b036f8b937f"], "had246643g1450g49e6g81e1g3bb0d95739a7": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "97379a69-0187-4aae-aeb8-6b036f8b937f"], "h51055b92gf87fg44adgaecfg269396e4668e": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "97379a69-0187-4aae-aeb8-6b036f8b937f"], "h034c576dga9eag4656gac3bg9ec6e90caf97": ["| Well we don't need to decide right now. (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "97379a69-0187-4aae-aeb8-6b036f8b937f"], "h4f4d2b83g9952g4e1cgb8f5g61bedfeee584": ["| Well we don't need to decide right now. (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "97379a69-0187-4aae-aeb8-6b036f8b937f"], "h3eed69abga610g44ecg8ac6g65190413d73d": ["Perhaps its best to stop debating in mixed company.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "97379a69-0187-4aae-aeb8-6b036f8b937f"], "hec06a56eg0eb3g4ecega744g7699a9af1c5a": ["It's over and done. Let's make the best of it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "ec1e127d-c6bb-48ea-98e0-fd505e864eed"], "hc748c768gacf0g447egaea3g07ea7d1a34a7": ["The decision is made. We will deal with consequences as they arise.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "ec1e127d-c6bb-48ea-98e0-fd505e864eed"], "h56c3ee9fg5727g4abeg8820g0352a446686f": ["Well, the important thing is you all agree.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "ec1e127d-c6bb-48ea-98e0-fd505e864eed"], "h1b49dac1gacbdg461ag9051g41e837317a94": ["Well if we're all in agreement, there's nothing more to discuss.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "ec1e127d-c6bb-48ea-98e0-fd505e864eed"], "hec2c1d8ag8086g495eg859bgf8add753bb81": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "ec1e127d-c6bb-48ea-98e0-fd505e864eed"], "hdf15e848ga332g4803gbf6eg922e1f557faa": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "ec1e127d-c6bb-48ea-98e0-fd505e864eed"], "h57dd5181g8f9bg428bgb1d0ga9d94d4ada00": ["| We are in agreement: A. (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "ec1e127d-c6bb-48ea-98e0-fd505e864eed"], "h84b673e8gd254g45d5gac38gdfd336266982": ["| We are in agreement: A. (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "ec1e127d-c6bb-48ea-98e0-fd505e864eed"], "h9158d88dg303bg4a32g9b84g2eaf3d44e6fa": ["Everyone's safe for now. Let's hope it stays that way.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "ec1e127d-c6bb-48ea-98e0-fd505e864eed"], "h592508ebg9de4g499ega4eag53c1b922e767": ["Good to know we're looking out for each other.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "9c0ca82e-80a1-42e0-bfaa-546df32b5f75"], "h0d219bf6g8522g4082gbe64gacd74d90f0d7": ["The decision is made. Let us hope Astarion keeps his fangs to himself.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "9c0ca82e-80a1-42e0-bfaa-546df32b5f75"], "h5c8282dbg2185g42adg82b0gf83164283d14": ["I'm flattered, but here's hoping it won't come up again.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "9c0ca82e-80a1-42e0-bfaa-546df32b5f75"], "h4e3194ebgb030g4633ga537g732bbe1788b8": ["If only we had such clarity <i>before </i>we decided to keep Astarion around. Oh well.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "9c0ca82e-80a1-42e0-bfaa-546df32b5f75"], "hfe8b1a87g0fbfg4a2eg920dg5c2b169e0e56": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "9c0ca82e-80a1-42e0-bfaa-546df32b5f75"], "h0a026049g6b65g43b8ga6c5ga641bc4a4362": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "9c0ca82e-80a1-42e0-bfaa-546df32b5f75"], "h7daf9b21geef1g41c1g8435gc3a86cc6ffb1": ["| We are in agreement: B. (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "9c0ca82e-80a1-42e0-bfaa-546df32b5f75"], "hf0336bbbgd72ag4c08gb844g007106bd6ef3": ["| We are in agreement: B. (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "9c0ca82e-80a1-42e0-bfaa-546df32b5f75"], "hbf9c4e2bge0a6g4234gb7efg73eb61dd1586": ["Protecting Astarion was the right thing to do. Let's move on.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "9c0ca82e-80a1-42e0-bfaa-546df32b5f75"], "h625d57efge29ag4136g8ef6ge3af79d57a31": ["I don't know... a vampire among us? It doesn't sit right.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "fdd38430-33df-47f1-a83c-104fdb8cab32"], "h35d74f06g01b0g444dg8ea7g345356b14121": ["Astarion is an unstable element. So long as he stays, we are in peril.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "fdd38430-33df-47f1-a83c-104fdb8cab32"], "hc33bf3adg74ffg4e2dg854bgd2efeaf25762": ["| I disagree. I want option A (Asterion Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "fdd38430-33df-47f1-a83c-104fdb8cab32"], "h8d9b630eg1b01g47dcgb799g8204f6a5d081": ["No. That was a perfect opportunity to rid ourselves of a dangerous liability, and we botched it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "fdd38430-33df-47f1-a83c-104fdb8cab32"], "h03597dd1g2617g4942g9411g03f025316e8a": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "fdd38430-33df-47f1-a83c-104fdb8cab32"], "h53ef1e2cg66adg4a9fg984fga4657597a03d": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_ProtectedAstarion.html", "fdd38430-33